OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob
OL,4,CGravells
OL,6,FBob Gravells, Age 99, Royal Navy
OL,8,FInterviewed 19 March 2024
OL,10,FConscripted aged just 18 and choosing
OL,11,Fthe Navy, Mr Gravells was on a
OL,12,Fmerchant ship carrying American troops
OL,13,Fto the beaches on the afternoon of D-
OL,14,FDay.
OL,16,FMotor Vessel Erna was a free Dutch
OL,17,Fship with a Dutch crew and he was a
OL,18,Fgunner.
OL,20,FMr Gravells said: "The weather was bad
OL,21,Fand the invasion was delayed.
