OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob
OL,4,CGravells
OL,6,F"During that time we took on board my
OL,7,Frecollection is 68 American soldiers -
OL,8,Fwonderful chaps they were.
OL,10,F"All around my age - 19,20,21, and the
OL,11,FDutch crew all spoke English.
OL,13,F"The Americans were on the ship for at
OL,14,Fleast three days and as you can
OL,15,Fimagine their accommodation wasn't
OL,16,Fgreat. It was in the hold."
OL,18,FDefensively equipped merchant ships or
OL,19,FDEMS had anti aircraft cannon normally
OL,20,Fmanned by military personnel.
