OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob
OL,4,CGravells
OL,6,FMr Gravells said: "All the ships were
OL,7,Ffiring at it but it was a bit out of
OL,8,Frange at first. As it came towards me
OL,9,Fin my range I opened fire on it.
OL,11,F"As it was right over the top of us it
OL,12,Fburst into flames.
OL,14,F"The pilot would have had no chance at
OL,15,Fall, and it spiralled out of control
OL,16,Fand crashed.
OL,18,F"They went off and they disappeared
OL,19,Ffrom view and we never saw or heard
OL,20,Ffrom them anymore,.
