OL,3,CD-Day 80 The Last Veterans: Bob
OL,4,CGravells
OL,6,F"The real fighting had been on the
OL,7,Fbeach. There were bodies floating
OL,8,Fabout in the sea when we arrived. We
OL,9,Fcouldn't get that close but we could
OL,10,Fsee. It was quiet. To the best of my
OL,11,Fknowledge, and no-one ever told us and
OL,12,Fit was dusky at the time, it was
OL,13,FOmaha."
OL,15,FWith light fading, the crew returned
OL,16,Fto Portsmouth to pick up British
OL,17,Ftroops who they then ferried to Sword
OL,18,Fbeach.
